            "content": "<p>Use it anywhere you need light cushioning and low-profile protection:</p><ul><li>Blisters and hot spots</li><li>Minor cuts and scrapes</li><li>Heels, toes, fingers, and elbows</li><li>Callused or pressure-prone skin</li><li>Superficial pressure areas that need a protective barrier</li></ul>",
