    "facebook_testimonials_product_gallery": {
      "type": "facebook-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "column_1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Rachel Tan",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/1659280289078.jpg",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "1 day ago",
            "post_text": "<p>I didn’t expect something this simple to make such a big difference in my skin!</p><p>It’s super thin and nearly invisible once applied, but the results are amazing overnight. I use it on active breakouts and it helps calm redness, protect the area, and speed up healing without leaving marks behind. It also stays in place through showers, sleep, and even sweaty days.</p><p>No more picking, no more scabs—just clearer, calmer skin. I also love that I can cut it into any size I need, which makes it so easy to use anywhere.</p><p></p><p>Definitely would repurchase!</p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_fbc77339-4787-4f37-8219-f86b7cdc2bb4.png",
            "post_reactions": "like, love, care",
            "post_reactions_text": "2.2k",
            "post_comments_text": "125 Comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_1_author_verified": false,
            "comment_1_time": "2h ago",
            "comment_1_text": "",
            "comment_2_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_2_author_verified": false,
            "comment_2_time": "3h ago",
            "comment_2_text": ""
          }
        },
        "column_2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Celina Katherine",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/pngtree-portrait-of-a-beautiful-european-woman-png-image_17955136.png",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "22 hours ago",
            "post_text": "<p>This hydrocolloid roll has completely changed how I deal with breakouts!</p><p>I cut small pieces and place them over any spots before sleeping. It stays on all night, even if I move around a lot, and it doesn’t peel off or feel uncomfortable at all.</p><p>By morning, redness looks calmer, swelling goes down, and the area feels protected so I’m not tempted to touch it. My skin heals faster and looks much cleaner after just a few uses.</p><p>It’s super thin, nearly invisible, and easy to cut into any size I need. Perfect for cheeks, chin, or anywhere random pimples pop up. </p><p>Definitely keeping this in my skincare routine!</p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/4d891765-9d32-4f4c-9b03-10396f181df9.png",
            "post_reactions": "like, love, care",
            "post_reactions_text": "836",
            "post_comments_text": "92 comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_1_author_verified": false,
            "comment_1_time": "2h ago",
            "comment_1_text": "",
            "comment_2_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_2_author_verified": false,
            "comment_2_time": "3h ago",
            "comment_2_text": ""
          }
        },
        "column_3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Marke Angelina",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/a30e75b889a9367cdc09531b47f7e552.jpg",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "7 hours ago",
            "post_text": "<p>This hydrocolloid roll is a total skincare must-have!</p><p>It’s incredibly thin and almost invisible on the skin, but works like magic overnight. I use it on active breakouts and it helps reduce redness, protect the spot, and speed up healing—without leaving any marks behind. It stays in place through showers, sleep, and even sweaty days without peeling off or sliding around.</p><p>No more picking, no more scabs—just clearer, calmer skin. I’ve noticed my spots look flatter, less irritated, and much less noticeable by the next morning. It creates a protective barrier so I’m not tempted to touch the area during the day.</p><p>Super convenient, comfortable, and effective! 💖</p><p></p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/cf893c28-29c6-4ab6-a4f0-59d5edc79467.png",
            "post_reactions": "like, care, love",
            "post_reactions_text": "1.4k",
